<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/264264051">http是应用层，ip是网络层，那么http请求头部的client ip是怎么获取到的呢？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="80944911"
data-atoken="279818958"
